description:
Imagine going to work everyday to a job you absolutely love. Imagine a life where you are completely fulfilled by the work you do, the people you help, and the environment you do it in.

This course contains videos, slideshows, worksheets, and bonus challenges to help you cut through the details and ineffective strategies and find your purpose. This course will teach you methods to break through the mental barriers that are holding you back to find a job that turns your purpose into profit.

You'll learn how to get out of your comfort zone, create a digital brand that gets you noticed, how to build and maintain a network that works to your advantage, and walk away with a one year action plan that outlines the steps you need to take on your personal journey to finding the purpose that fuels your career.
title: Find Purpose in Your Career
